# 🚀 NexusDeploy Enterprise CI/CD Platform

## 📌 Project Overview

**NexusDeploy** is a production-grade DevOps CI/CD automation platform designed to streamline the entire software delivery lifecycle—from code commit to production deployment.

This project demonstrates how modern DevOps teams automate:

* Source Code Management
* Continuous Integration (CI)
* Code Quality Analysis
* Security Scanning
* Containerization
* Container Registry Management
* Continuous Deployment (CD)
* Monitoring & Observability

The platform automatically builds, tests, scans, packages, and deploys applications whenever developers push code to GitHub.

