# 🚀 Getting Started

## Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/im-ganesh/nexusdeploy.git
cd nexusdeploy
```

## Configure Jenkins

* Install required plugins
* Configure GitHub webhook
* Setup SonarQube integration
* Configure Docker and AWS credentials

## Deploy Infrastructure

```bash
terraform init
terraform plan
terraform apply
```

## Trigger Pipeline

Push code to GitHub and watch the entire CI/CD pipeline execute automatically.

